{100}{}{Santiago}
{200}{}{You see the CIA chief.}
{200}{}{It's Santiago, Chief of the NCR Counter Intelligence Agency.}
{210}{}{Santiago, one of Shaiman's foremen. They both arrived to NCR from the Hub in 2246.}
{210}{}{It's Santiago. He's responsible for internal security and field intelligence of the capital.}
{1000}{}{Predialogue installations}
{1010}{}{низкий инт}
{1020}{}{норм инт}
{2000}{}{[Santiago is surprised to see you] If you're here, it must be necessary. What happened?}
{2010}{}{I won't waste your time. [Leave]}
{2020}{}{Greetings. I heard you're looking for a reliable man, is it true?}
{2030}{}{Santiago, I finished your assignment. [Hand him the recorder]}
{2040}{}{I'd like to offer my services to your department.}
{2050}{}{I'd like to offer my services to your department.}
{2060}{}{I'd like to offer my services to your department.}
{2070}{}{I asked around NCR citizens.}
{2080}{}{Santiago, I found out who was causing a stir.}
{2090}{}{Mr. Santiago, I know who's Bishop's man in NCR.}
{3000}{}{Leave this building at once.}
{4000}{}{I've heard a lot about you. Hell, Shaiman himself speaks in your favor. Yes, I have a responsible assignment, for which we could use your outstanding talents.}
{4010}{}{What do I got to do?}
{5000}{}{Say, It's a covert op. The Republic needs to be aware of what's cooking in the wasteland. In this case, in Vault City.}
{5010}{}{How can I be of service?}
{6000}{}{You will be issued special equipment. Then you'll infiltrate Vault City and record the annual report of one of the Councilmen to Lynette.}
{6010}{}{When is the report due to take place?}
{7000}{}{Every day at 1800. Needless to say you must not be spotted. If you are discovered, the operation is considered failed. Questions?}
{7010}{}{I need time to make decision.}
{7020}{}{No questions, sir. I'm ready to begin.}
{8000}{}{Don't be too long, the operation is urgent.}
{8010}{}{Goodbye.}
